item.title: About Me
item.description: I am an aspiring malware analyst/researcher. My intention for this blog is to create a place to post my attempts at reverse engineering and malware analysis. If you like the content, or want to correct any mistakes I may have made, feel free to contact me at mithrandir@defcon.social.
item.content:
